==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Khond
<hw>Khond</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A Dravidian of a group
of tribes of Orissa, India, a section of whom were formerly noted for
their cruel human sacrifices to the earth goddess, murder of female
infants, and marriage by capture.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Khutbah</ent>⟦br⟧
